---
title: Quote y Compra Presencial Orquestados
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Alumno
    participant BFF
    participant API as API pública
    participant App as api:app Orchestrator
    participant Billing as Billing Core
    participant Physical as Physical Core
    participant MP as Mercado Pago

    Alumno->>BFF: Elegir MONTHLY o una sesión INDIVIDUAL
    BFF->>API: POST /api/v1/billing/physical-course-quotes
    API->>App: CreatePhysicalQuote(command)
    App->>Billing: Obtener pricing versionado
    App->>Physical: Consultar sesiones/capacidad
    Physical-->>App: SessionSnapshot[]
    App->>Billing: Persistir un quote de una modalidad
    Billing-->>App: quoteId, coverageStartDate, sessionIds, total, expiresAt
    App-->>API: Quote persistido
    API-->>BFF: Quote MONTHLY o INDIVIDUAL

    Alumno->>BFF: Iniciar Purchase antes del vencimiento
    BFF->>API: POST /api/v1/billing/physical-purchases {quoteId}
    API->>App: StartPhysicalPurchase
    App->>Physical: Crear CapacityHold técnico
    Physical-->>App: holdId
    App->>Billing: Crear Purchase PAYMENT_PENDING y Payment PENDING
    Billing->>MP: Crear checkout con purchaseId
    MP-->>Billing: paymentUrl
    Billing-->>App: purchaseId, paymentUrl
    App-->>API: Purchase
    API-->>BFF: purchaseId, paymentUrl, state firmado

    Note over Alumno,Physical: Sin reserva manual ni lista de espera

